<item>
            <title>[LU-7108] Remove sanityn tests 14b, 19, 29, and 35 from the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7108</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ALWAYS_EXCEPT list for sanityn was recently truncated by mistake and all the tests on that list were run for all patches submitted to the master branch. All the tests on sanityn&#8217;s ALWAYS_EXCEPT list ran about 40 times all with no errors except for test_28 (see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-7105&quot; title=&quot;sanityn test_28 fails with &amp;#39;error() without useful message, please fix&amp;#39;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-7105&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-7105&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;). Since tests 14b, 19, 29, and 35 ran with no failures, please remove them from the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list. &lt;/p&gt;

